snippet.title: UnblockHex Promo
snippet.description:
Puzzle-style games Tag. Has several types of playing fields and increasing difficulty of levels.
The game has a rating system. Raise your level and compete with your friends.
This puzzle is great recharging your brain.

GooglePlay - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wooloofun.unblockhex
AppStore - https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/unblock-hex/id1200432188?ls=1&mt=8
